  <summary date="2024-03-11T20:12:17Z" status="Introduced in House">Creating Hope Reauthorization Act of 2024

This bill extends until FY2029 a Food and Drug Administration program that awards priority review vouchers to manufacturers of drugs that treat rare pediatric diseases. (A priority review voucher entitles the voucher holder to priority review of a single human drug application.)</summary>
